| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5785 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7ceb2023-01b4-5be2-b3fb-71a3c6f4bc88"
